<paragraph id="D37C0A04F5B82A135DEEC3C87F0B06A8" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D9187305470EAC72D24B7FFC6216A9C3" pageId="0" pageNumber="87">Pileus dark brown at center, covered with dark brown fibrillose or pubescent. Stipe densely pruinose when young. Cheilocystidia present. Pileus trama with visible dark brown hyphae and coarse excrescences.</paragraph>
